Cell[TextData[{
 "In addition to the noise filter, we can remove observations from the \
dataset that have been contaminated by background radiation. ",
 Cell[BoxData["getIObsKeep"], "MCode"],
 " returns the indices of the observations in ",
 Cell[BoxData["dat"], "MCode"],
 " that should not be thrown out, based on the parameters ",
 Cell[BoxData["peakPosCut"], "MCode"],
 ", ",
 Cell[BoxData["peakValCut"], "MCode"],
 ", and ",
 Cell[BoxData["peakNumCut"], "MCode"],
 " that characterize waveforms unduly influenced by background radiation. The \
graphical output is a random sample of rejected observations."
}], "Text",
