      FontSlant->"Plain"], 
     StyleBox["1",
      FontSlant->"Plain"]}]}], TraditionalForm]], "Math"],
 ". (Throughout this theorem, the top symbol of a plus-or-minus sign \
indicates the addition of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
