  RowBox[{"\[LeftDoubleBracket]", 
   RowBox[{"i", ",", "j"}], "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}]], "MCode"],
 " is the mean square deviation of observation ",
 Cell[BoxData["j"], "MCode"],
 " from the mean trace of cluster ",
 Cell[BoxData["i"], "MCode"],
 "."
}], "Text",
