    RowBox[{"OutputForm", "[", 
     RowBox[{"StringJoin", "[", 
      RowBox[{"Map", "[", 
       RowBox[{"ToString", ",", 
        RowBox[{"{", "args", "}"}]}], "]"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",", "iRun", ",", 
    "\"\<Log\>\""}], "]"}]}]], "Input",
